{"tid":2413840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"趁雪打劫？德州寒流大停電 民眾電費暴漲超過100倍｢一天逾12萬元｣","createTime":"2021-02-19T04:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T19:46:24.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c338768b2b10da1ab1e80985ee18393b9c823a50","tid":2413840,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"美國破紀錄的冬季風暴肆虐德州，低溫酷寒之下還發生大停電，有400多萬戶家庭和企業<br />\n無電可用，讓民眾苦不堪言，而天價般昂貴的電費，更讓消費者的苦難「雪上加霜」；經<br />\n營護膚兼藥材店的43歲德州婦人史考特-艾默斯（Akilah Scott-Amos）周末期間突然接到<br />\n電力公司網迪（Griddy）簡訊告知，她的帳單已「快要破表」，建議更換別家。<br />\n <br />\n史考特-艾默斯17日接受新聞網站「野獸日報」（Daily Beast）訪問時說：「我的電費竟<br />\n一天就達450美元（約新台幣12.5萬元），我嚇壞了。」她想不通為何電費這麼高，因為<br />\n家裡使用瓦斯加熱器、瓦斯壁爐，並把室內溫度控制在華氏65度，若以電費帳單價格來看<br />\n，彷彿「幫整個社區照亮到燈火通明」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-19/538272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-02-19%2F538272&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69PaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=6d9a61eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-19/538272</a>"},{"pid":"d36336e090b52cfebf9b13c52bc01b3d542d0b93","tid":2413840,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"華氏65度等於18.333333333333332攝氏度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3fc07479ade486cd1120f09e23d1101e8f60c2","tid":2413840,"uid":107620,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"google咗1USD=27.95NTD<br />\n450USD=12577.5NTD<br />\n<br />\n12萬5NTD？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5422e537893624532531a668ff1228d9b393e48","tid":2413840,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3fc07479ade486cd1120f09e23d1101e8f60c2","tid":2413840,"uid":107620,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"google咗1US